        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer340631899" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11300717377264675440">This book is pretty messed up. It contains graphic descriptions of murder, mutilation, and sexual assault. But it is one of the most important books I&apos;ve ever read. Locking people up and throwing away the key, to borrow a phrase from a previous review, is never the answer. See: Attica, Alcatraz, Fremantle, Strangeways, San Quentin, Ciudad Juarez, Apodaca, and most recently in a facility holding illegal immigrants in Mississippi. It will keep happening, as sure as the sun will continue to rise an</span>
  <span id="freeText11300717377264675440" style="display:none">This book is pretty messed up. It contains graphic descriptions of murder, mutilation, and sexual assault. But it is one of the most important books I've ever read. Locking people up and throwing away the key, to borrow a phrase from a previous review, is never the answer. See: Attica, Alcatraz, Fremantle, Strangeways, San Quentin, Ciudad Juarez, Apodaca, and most recently in a facility holding illegal immigrants in Mississippi. It will keep happening, as sure as the sun will continue to rise and set, when we treat people like animals, pit them against each other for our own sadistic pleasure, and deny them their basic human rights.</span>
